dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S 4374. Alternate title: Derna city plan. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. Lybia zone grid. Relief shown by hachures. Compiled by 512 Fd. Survey Coy., R.E., October 1941, from air photographs dated June 1941. Names based on Italian town plan. Revised from air photographs dated October 1942, and reprinted October, 1942.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
